                     <interp inst="t18180401-46-person356" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker, and live in Fetter-lane. I have two sheet, a waistcoat, and a gown which were pledged with me.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. It is my first offence. I beg for mercy.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18180401-46-verdict269" type="verdictDescription">
